$ Accessing Avaloq with Visual Basic for Applications

A few VBA → development/languages/VBA/language/classes[classes] and modules to connect to an → Companies-Products/Avaloq[Avaloq] database with → development/languages/VBA[Visual Basic for Application]
so that Avaloq related data can be used in → Microsoft/Office/Excel[Excel] or other → Microsoft/Office[Office] applications.

{ Avaloq.bas

  gh|Avaloq-VBA|/Avaloq.bas||

}
{ avqObj.cls

  gh|Avaloq-VBA|/obj/avqObj.cls||

}
{ avqCont.cls

  gh|Avaloq-VBA|/obj/avqCont.cls||

}
